# Node modules (todas as pastas)
**/node_modules

# Builds do Nuxt (não precisa no Docker, são gerados no build)
**/.output
**/.nuxt
**/.nitro
**/.cache
**/dist

# Logs
**/logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Arquivos de ambiente (não fazer commit de secrets!)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Arquivos de sistema
**/.DS_Store
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.fleet

# Temporários
**/tmp
**/temp
**/*.tmp
**/*.swp
**/*.swo

# Coverage e testes
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/test-results

# Backups
**/*.orig
**/*.BACKUP.*
**/*.BASE.*
**/*.LOCAL.*
**/*.REMOTE.*
**/app/services/backup/backups

# Fly.io
fly.toml
.dockerignore
README.md
.github/
scripts/deploy.sh